8 Hours Ago However, spokesperson for the police in the state, Suleiman Nguroje, could not confirm the fatalities. He said, "Detectives have not returned from the area, so I cannot confirm any fatality. "But I can confirm that we have so far arrested 32 people in connection with the violence."